""" "get" shouldn't be called until the value is *dereferenced* """
c = Configure()
a = {'t': False}
class pipe(ConfigValue):

    def get(self):
        a['t'] = True
        return 'sign'
c['seven'] = pipe()
self.assertFalse(a['t'])
self.assertEqual(c['seven'], 'sign')
self.assertTrue(a['t'])
